1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
 molim vas sjednite.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:05,000
 Kako se osjećate večeras?

3
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
 Tired?

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,000
 Jel možemo nastaviti do dva ujutro?

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
 To je super.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
 Ujutro da je mnogo mladih među nama.

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
 Mnogo mnogo mnogo mnogo.

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,000
 Mnogo mnogo mnogo mnogo.

9
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:40,000
 I to je ujutro da smo mnogo mnogo mnogo.

10
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:56,000
 Prije nego što započnem svoje sljedeće predavanje,

11
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:03,000
 želim dovršiti prethodni nagovor.

12
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:08,000
 Ja sam morao prekinuti radi vremena.

13
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:14,000
 Dakle, još jednom želim samo naglasiti važnost zagovaranja.

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:28,000
 Većinu vremena mi uopće neslećamo važnost zagovaranja.

15
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:32,000
 Tome sjedućimo u crkvi.

16
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:36,000
 Vidimo to u obnovi.

17
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:50,000
 I čak sam uvidio da većina naših voditelja nisu uvjereni u važnost zagovaranja.

18
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:55,000
 Ako uzmete za primjer crkvu,

19
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:00,000
 želim vam dati jedno objašnjenje.

20
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:07,000
 Ovaj kišobran, zamislite ga daje on kao crkva.

21
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:12,000
 Zamislite, ovo je crkva.

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:18,000
 Dakle, crkva ima nekoliko različitih službi.

23
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:25,000
 Dakle, ima tu svoju službu koja je religijska služba.

24
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:36,000
 Služba koja je obrazovanje, dakle crkva nekad vodi univerzitete, nekad sve učilišta, nekad škole.

25
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:42,000
 Ima također službu zdravstvenu.

26
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:47,000
 Neke bolnice su pod crkvom.

27
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:50,000
 Možda različiti centri.

28
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:54,000
 Onda imate socijalni rad.

29
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:57,000
 To poznajte vrlo dobro.

30
00:02:57,000 --> 00:03:02,000
 Onda imate službu evangelizacije.

31
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:09,000
 Dakle, ima različiti službi koje su unutar crkve.

32
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:18,000
 Ali ima nešto zbog čega je ovaj kišobran uspravan.

33
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:24,000
 Dakle, to je ovaj stup, stup kišobrana.

34
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:32,000
 Bez ovog stupa, ni ove žice ne bi mogle stajati tu.

35
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:43,000
 A što je, dakle, za svaku od ovih službi stup, to je zagovor.

36
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:53,000
 Kako bi svaka od ovih pojedinačnih službi funkcionirala, mora postojati zagovor.

37
00:03:54,000 --> 00:04:04,000
 Samo preko toga će sve službe u crkvi biti učinkovite i plodonosne.

38
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
 Mnogi od nas na to zaboravimo.

39
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:15,000
 I vjerujemo kako su naši projekti,

40
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:20,000
 sa svom našom inteligencijom, umom i znanjem,

41
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:24,000
 se mogu primijeniti,

42
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:28,000
 sa svim našim izvorima,

43
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:34,000
 dakle, snagom koju imamo kao ljudi, posjedujemo s novcem,

44
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:39,000
 mi mislimo da mi možemo postići rezultate.

45
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:46,000
 Ali naši projekti neće donijeti ploda,

46
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:52,000
 jer ne zagovaramo dovoljno.

47
00:04:54,000 --> 00:05:00,000
 Spomenuo sam vam Svetog Benedikta.

48
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:09,000
 Sveti Benedikt je imao moto, geslo,

49
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:13,000
 osam sati radite, ali osam sati molite.

50
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:24,000
 Mnoge kongregacije, vijerske zajednice, u početku, kada su začete,

51
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:28,000
 na um je bio da one budu kontemplativne zajednice.

52
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:31,000
 Oni su trebali moliti.

53
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,000
 i nisam sve od nisam,

54
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,000
 kodne konjugacije,

55
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,000
 koji su aktive,

56
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,000
 ali u samom,

57
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:41,000
 je u drugom konjugacije,

58
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,000
 koji su kontemplativne.

59
00:05:57,000 --> 00:06:10,000
 Dva sveca je crkva preglasila zaštitnicima misionarskog djelovanja.

60
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:16,000
 Zaštitnicima evangelizacije.

61
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:20,000
 Znate da koji su to sveci?

62
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,520
 St. Francis the sails

63
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,740
 and St. Therese

64
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:28,600
 someone was saying.

65
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,940
 St. Francis saviour and

66
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:37,880
 St. Francis the sails, they said.

67
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,380
 No, no.

68
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,000
 It's not him.

69
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,140
 St. Francis saviour and

70
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:46,580
 St. Therese.

71
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,100
 St. Therese.

72
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:50,220
 The two saints are

73
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,060
 St. Francis saviour

74
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:54,820
 and St. Therese of little flower.

75
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:59,760
 Yeah, she is there.

76
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:08,040
 You know, when I heard this for the first time,

77
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:11,860
 I thought to myself.

78
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:15,240
 The church is very foolish.

79
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:19,020
 You know why?

80
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:24,040
 Because St. Francis saviour

81
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,520
 travelled from Europe to Asia

82
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:35,120
 he travelled to many countries that time

83
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:39,340
 he preached the gospel

84
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:43,020
 converted people

85
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:46,700
 baptized them

86
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:47,860
 baptized them

87
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:49,960
 and so

88
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:52,220
 he deserves to be

89
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:54,360
 the patron of missionary work

90
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:59,460
 but what about

91
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:00,860
 this little Therese?

92
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:06,860
 I know he died at the age of 24.

93
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,980
 Znate, imala je samo 24 godine

94
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:09,760
 kada je umrla.

95
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:12,520
 There is nothing that says that she

96
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:15,780
 travelled to any place to priest God's word.

97
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:18,380
 Nigdje nemamo dokaza o tome kako je putovala

98
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:20,500
 u neka mjesta u kojima je evangelizirala

99
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,820
 ili nosila Kristov nauk.

100
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:25,360
 She joined a Cloysted convent.

101
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:28,060
 Pridružila je sa zatvorenom samostanu.

102
00:08:28,060 --> 00:08:30,040
 Do you understand what is Cloysted?

103
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,540
 Znate što znači zatvoreni samostan?

104
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:33,340
 Yeah.

105
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:36,220
 Once you go inside, you don't come out.

106
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:38,000
 Jednom kad uđeš u taj samostan

107
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,900
 nema izlaska.

108
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:41,600
 And then we say that

109
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:44,360
 she is patroness of missionary work.

110
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:50,940
 How does she deserve

111
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:53,520
 to be the patroness of missionary work?

112
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,560
 Kako je ona zaslužila taj naziv?

113
00:08:55,560 --> 00:09:02,660
 She interceded, they're saying.

114
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:04,460
 She interceded.

115
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:06,060
 You're right.

116
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,480
 U pravu ste.

117
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:12,680
 You know, she was a tuberculosis patient.

118
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:16,660
 Dakle, ona je bila jako blizu misionarima.

119
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:20,540
 Iako je umrla jako mlada.

120
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:25,440
 But she prayed and prayed and prayed

121
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:28,280
 ali ona je stalno molila i molila i molila

122
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:35,700
 možda zadnji dan ako budemo imali vremena

123
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:39,300
 daću vam više podataka o tome kako je točno ona zagovarala.

124
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:42,200
 So by appointing these two saints

125
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:45,520
 dakle, to dvoje svetaca su imenovani zaštetnicima.

126
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:52,260
 Sveti Franju Ksaverski koji je bio jako aktivan u svojoj službi.

127
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,660
 Ksavers, Ksavers, Ksavers.

128
00:09:55,660 --> 00:10:01,580
 Ajme, ja se ispričavam Ksaverski.

129
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:07,820
 Da, ja to kažem, ali zvuči drugačije.

130
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:27,420
 Dakle, sveti Franju Ksaverski koji je bio aktivan i koji je molio u svom misionarskom djelovanju.

131
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:37,720
 I druga svetica Tereza od djeteta Isusa kao druga zaštetnica.

132
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:41,400
 I crkva nam govori

133
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:53,680
 kako je evangelizacija nije moguća osim kroz izličito navještanje.

134
00:10:53,680 --> 00:11:05,360
 Misjonarska služba nije moguća osim ako ne djelujete i ako konkretna djela ne činite u tome.

135
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:09,660
 Ako trebate evangelizirati

136
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:14,640
 Ako je potrebno da ste u misjonarskoj službi

137
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:19,260
 mora postojati zagovaranje.

138
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:24,000
 Dakle, to trebamo shvatiti.

139
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:30,840
 Vođe u obnovi trebaju ovo shvatiti.

140
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:36,380
 Također vođe u crkvi trebaju shvatiti isto.

141
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:47,720
 I još jednom želim naglasiti zašto je zagovaranje jako, jako bitno.

142
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,960
 Amen.

143
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:56,860
 Sad idemo na sljedeću poglavlje.

144
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:05,440
 Dakle, ovdje se radi o zagovarniku koji je se pokajao.

145
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:16,660
 Dakle, ovdje se radi o jedina pouka koja se ne radi, jer nije samo riječ o zagovaranju.

146
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:22,860
 Ali vas priprema za zagovaranje.

147
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:28,600
 Zagovaranje je nešto što je jako moćno.

148
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:35,660
 I putem zagovaranja vi ćete dobiti različite stvari.

149
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:46,520
 Ali u zagovaranju ono što je stvarno bitno je naš vlastiti odnos s Bogom.

150
00:12:46,860 --> 00:12:52,740
 Zagovaratelj postaje posrednik.

151
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:59,700
 Vi ste onaj koji je posrednik između ljudi i Boga.

152
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:04,100
 Bilo od kod ko je posrednik

153
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:15,940
 mora uživati u tom odnosu između jedne i druge strane.

154
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:23,800
 Dakle, morate imati dobar odnos s ljudima za koje zagovarate.

155
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:33,360
 I također morate imati dobar odnos s Bogom pred kojim ćete zagovarati za njih.

156
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:45,680
 Dakle, to je trostruka molitva koja uključuje tri osobe.

157
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:54,980
 Kad vi zagovarate, vaše molitve su upućene Otcu.

158
00:13:54,980 --> 00:14:03,280
 Svoju molitvu govorite preko Isusa Hrista.

159
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:08,200
 Jer je On taj koji je zagovarnik.

160
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:15,900
 a vi zagovarate snagom Duha Svetoga.

161
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:25,640
 Kada zagovarate, sve tri osobe presvedog trojstva su uključene.

162
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:36,200
 I zato sam vam rekao kako je zagovaranje jako bitna molitva i moćna molitva.

163
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:44,960
 Ne smijemo misliti kako je zagovaranje nešto što je samo za slabiće.

164
00:14:44,960 --> 00:15:03,860
 Svi vi ovdje koji ste u službi, koji imate službu zagovaranja, želi vam potvrditi kako činite nešto što je jako bitno, jako, jako, jako snažno.

165
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:10,140
 Svi vi koji ste u službi zagovaranja ovdje, podignite svoje ruke.

166
00:15:10,140 --> 00:15:23,300
 Ja, i zato sam da je pola vas zagovaratelji, zaplješćemo svima vama.

167
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:36,020
 Vi činite nešto što je jako bitno i jako, jako snažno.

168
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:43,140
 Dakle, budući ste uključeni u nešto što je jako bitno,

169
00:15:43,140 --> 00:15:52,480
 jako je bitno da mi imamo pravu odgovornost pred Bogom.

170
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:58,860
 Dakle, u knjizi Postanka, 18. poglavlje,

171
00:15:58,860 --> 00:16:07,580
 prvi odjeljak koji se nalazi u Svetoj Bibliji, a odnosi se na zagovaranje,

172
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:11,760
 Božja riječ nam jasno kazuje

173
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:18,460
 da dok se Abraham spremao da zagovara,

174
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:25,120
 on se što više, još više približavao Bogu.

175
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:27,760
 Svaki zagovaratelj,

176
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:32,180
 kada započinje zagovarati,

177
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:37,060
 mi se automatski približavamo Bogu.

178
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:41,980
 Ali dok se još približavamo Bogu,

179
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:48,620
 kao što možemo vidjeti u knjizi izlazka u trećem poglavlju,

180
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:53,440
 kada je Mojs je vidio gorući grn,

181
00:16:54,100 --> 00:17:03,980
 on je bio zadivljen jer je tu bila vatra, ali grm nije izgarao.

182
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:10,560
 I Mojs je se primakao u tom gorućem grmu

183
00:17:10,560 --> 00:17:15,160
 i gospodin je progovorio iz grma,

184
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:17,660
 Mojs je,

185
00:17:17,660 --> 00:17:20,700
 ne približavaj se,

186
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:25,480
 izuj sandale, izuj obuću,

187
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:31,980
 jer mjesto na kojem stojiš, sve to je mjesto.

188
00:17:31,980 --> 00:17:39,280
 Svaki put kada se zagovaratelj približi Bogu,

189
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:42,480
 gospodin nas pocijeća

190
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:46,320
 kako trebamo izuti obuću,

191
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:50,500
 jer se nalazimo na svetom mjestu.

192
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:58,960
 jer dok zagovaramo, molimo u snazi Duha Svetoga,

193
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:03,120
 preko Isusa Hrista koji zagovara,

194
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:07,800
 i mi svoje molotve upućujemo Otcu.

195
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:19,440
 i tako se zagovaratelj povezuje i sjedinjuje s tri osobe presvetog trojstva.

196
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:28,120
 I prva stvar koju bi vam želio reći

197
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:31,260
 odnosi se na samo središte zagovaranja,

198
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:48,220
 Revelations, chapter 2, verses 2 to 5.

199
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:53,460
 Dakle, knjiga Otkrivenja, drugo poglavlje, redak 2 do 4.

200
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:55,000
 I will read.

201
00:18:56,900 --> 00:19:02,980
 Znam tvoja dijela, tvoj trud i postojanost tvoju,

202
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:06,080
 i da ne možeš podnijeti opak ih.

203
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:10,080
 Iskušao si one koji se prave apostolima, a nisu,

204
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:12,380
 i otkrio si da su lažljivci.

205
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:16,200
 Postojan si, podnio si za ime moje,

206
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:18,020
 i nisi smalaksao.

207
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:20,080
 Ali imam protiv tebe.

208
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:22,840
 Prvu si ljubav svoju ostavio.

209
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,120
 Spomeni se dakle, odakle si pao,

210
00:19:26,120 --> 00:19:29,040
 obrati se i čini prva dijela.

211
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:33,120
 Now, it begins like this.

212
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:34,420
 Počinje ovako.

213
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,960
 I know your works.

214
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,680
 Znam tvoja dijela.

215
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,280
 Your hard labor.

216
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:40,840
 Znam tvoj trud.

217
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,140
 Your endivarence.

218
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:43,920
 Znam postojanost tvoju.

219
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:46,980
 And you have been doing a marvelous job.

220
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:50,020
 I obavljao si izvrstan posao.

221
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:58,800
 Dakle, ovo je pismo koje je bilo upućeno crkvi u Efezu.

222
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:07,040
 I već znamo od prvog poglavlja knjige Otkrivenja

223
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:09,460
 da je Sveti Ivan bio pisac ove knjige.

224
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:17,040
 I on piše ovo pismo.

225
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:20,460
 Upućeno je sedam crkava.

226
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:25,680
 I on opisuje svoje iskustvo.

227
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:32,740
 I rekao je kako je sjedio na jednom otoku.

228
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:42,100
 I odjednom sam se okrenuo i čuo sam glas koji je mi je govorio.

229
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:47,420
 i taj glas mi je rekao da piši ovo pismo.

230
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:56,420
 I prvo od tih pisama je pismo crkvi u Efezu.

231
00:20:56,920 --> 00:21:09,040
 25 godina nakon što je vjera stigla u Efezu, on piše ovo pismo.

232
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:22,920
 Dakle, taj prvi dio pismo je više kao potvrda, potvrda svega što su oni već znali.

233
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:30,180
 Dakle, to je već potvrda onoga svega s čime su se oni složili.

234
00:21:30,180 --> 00:21:34,680
 Ali nakon toga kaže,

235
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:39,040
 četreti redak,

236
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:44,440
 ali imam protiv tebe.

237
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:53,340
 Prvu si ljubav svoju ostavio.

238
00:21:53,340 --> 00:22:03,620
 Dakle, 25 godina nakon što je vjera došla u Efezu,

239
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:11,340
 Duh Božji se obraća crkvi u Efezu

240
00:22:11,340 --> 00:22:19,380
 i kaže im, radili ste izvrsne, prekrasne stvari.

241
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:24,880
 Stvarno cijenim sav trud koji ste unijeli u to.

242
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:33,600
 Stvarno cijenim činjenicu da ste 25 godina iz 25 godina.

243
00:22:33,620 --> 00:22:35,380
 želi u postojanosti svoje vjere.

244
00:22:35,380 --> 00:22:39,020
 Yet, I have this against you.

245
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:42,520
 And what is it?

246
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:51,340
 That you lost the love you had at first.

247
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:53,340
 Izgubili ste svoju prvu ljubav.

248
00:22:53,340 --> 00:23:00,280
 Kada ste počeli, kada ste došli na život,

249
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:04,760
 Gospodin nam to govori danas.

250
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:12,720
 Kada ste vi započeli, kakva je bila vaša ljubav prema meni?

251
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:16,760
 Kada ste me prvi put upoznali,

252
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:21,880
 Možda je to bilo na seminaru obnove u Duhu,

253
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:27,760
 Nakon što ste iskusili krštenje u Duhu svetom,

254
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:33,060
 Gorili ste od ljubavi za mene.

255
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:36,820
 Bili ste jako strastveni.

256
00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:47,480
 I sjećam se svog prvog iskustva seminara obnove krštenja u Duhu.

257
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:50,960
 I kada sam se vratio doma,

258
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:56,940
 Osjećao sam se kao da sam lebdio.

259
00:23:56,940 --> 00:24:03,140
 Mao sam dojam da sam najsvetiji čovjek na zemlji.

260
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:08,100
 To je bilo tako jako, jako iskustvo.

261
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:14,380
 Moje srce je gorjelo od ljubavi prema Bogu.

262
00:24:14,380 --> 00:24:21,960
 I oni svi kažu kako je ta prva ljubav luda ljubav.

263
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:25,060
 Ta ljubav je strastvena.

264
00:24:25,060 --> 00:24:28,900
 Neki od vas se čak smiju.

265
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:33,920
 Jer oni znaju i razumiju što znači prva ljubav.

266
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:38,180
 Prva ljubav je nešto jako posebno.

267
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:42,180
 I ta ljubav nam kaže,

268
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:45,760
 sjeti se te prve ljubavi.

269
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:51,780
 Sjeti se onog dana kada si započeo.

270
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:56,100
 Sjeti se onog dana kada si me isprva upoznal.

271
00:24:56,100 --> 00:25:03,060
 Sjeti se svog osobnog odnosa koji si imao s Isusom.

272
00:25:03,060 --> 00:25:06,560
 kako smo bili strastveni.

273
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:12,640
 I kako smo, dakle, počeli strastveno, godljivo.

274
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:17,500
 kako smo se okrenuli prema Bogu.

275
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:23,900
 I u tom procesu smo započeli mnoge službe.

276
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:28,400
 Možda smo počeli, we began.

277
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:32,160
 počeli smo voditelji.

278
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:36,660
 I bili smo uključeni u svoje poslanje.

279
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:39,820
 Ali gospodin kaže,

280
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:42,600
 sa svim tim,

281
00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:50,240
 sa svim tim što ste radili,

282
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,820
 polako ste izgubili

283
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:53,840
 izvida svoju prvu ljubav.

284
00:25:53,840 --> 00:26:01,280
 To je nešto jako subtilno što se dogadi u našem životu.

285
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:06,660
 Dragi prijatelji,

286
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:08,360
 mi čak i ne svačavamo trenutak

287
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:10,020
 kada izgubimo tu prvu ljubav.

288
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:14,400
 Kad smo započeli,

289
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:16,620
 bili smo jako, jako, jako zagrijani.

290
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:19,620
 Bili smo jako vrući.

291
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:24,880
 I polako se počinjemo hladiti.

292
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,560
 A gospodin kaže,

293
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:31,780
 ako što ste bili vrući,

294
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:35,220
 onda kad postanete hladni,

295
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:40,040
 nećete postati jako hladni.

296
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:44,220
 Ostat ćete mlaki.

297
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:48,880
 I gospodin to naziva mlakošću.

298
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:53,840
 I u sljedećem poglavlju gospodin kaže,

299
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:57,740
 ispljenu ću te.

300
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:01,680
 Jer gospodin kaže,

301
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,000
 to mi se ne sviđa.

302
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:09,160
 I volio bih da si vruć ili da si hladan.

303
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:15,580
 Sada si u stanju koja je između toga dva stanja.

304
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:18,880
 Niti si vruć,

305
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:21,400
 niti si hladan.

306
00:27:21,400 --> 00:27:28,700
 To je jako bitno za zagovaratelje.

307
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:34,860
 Dakle, nitko ne može baš,

308
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:39,140
 ne može netko postati zagovaratelj.

309
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:48,260
 Osim ako vaše srce nije puno ljubavi za gospodina.

310
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:53,240
 Dakle, moje pitanje je,

311
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,300
 zašto bi mi onda trebali zagovaratelj?

312
00:27:55,540 --> 00:28:00,860
 Dakle, zagovaranje nije baš skroz pogodno.

313
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:05,400
 Ako već krećete u službu zagovaranja,

314
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:11,660
 morate žrtvovati dosta vašeg vremena.

315
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:18,060
 Nakon tjedana i tjedana rada,

316
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:20,700
 vikendom,

317
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:24,600
 možda se želite opustiti.

318
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:27,860
 Možda želite nedokreniti san.

319
00:28:27,860 --> 00:28:31,060
 Možda želite otići u kino.

320
00:28:31,060 --> 00:28:36,680
 A upravo je to vrijeme kada ćete zagovarati.

321
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:42,340
 i onda ćete dakle žrtvovati sve vaše odnose.

322
00:28:42,340 --> 00:28:45,500
 Zašto biste to učinili?

323
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:53,580
 Samo ako ste osoba koja izgara od ljubavi za Boga.

324
00:28:53,580 --> 00:29:03,260
 Samo ako ste osoba koja izgara od ljubavi za svoje sugrađane.

325
00:29:03,260 --> 00:29:07,600
 Recimo, vi ste u Hrvatskoj,

326
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:10,540
 u Bosni i Hercegovini,

327
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:18,260
 dogodi se da vi zagovarate za nekoga tko živi u Sjedinjenim državama.

328
00:29:18,260 --> 00:29:25,600
 Ta osoba nikad neće spoznati da ste vi zagovarali za nju.

329
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:35,280
 ta osoba nikad neće spoznati da ste vi bili ti koji ste zagovarali za nju ili za njega.

330
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:43,480
 Dakle, to je posao koji je bezvremenski.

331
00:29:43,820 --> 00:30:03,860
 Zbog toga mi moramo imati srce pravog zagovaratelja.

332
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:14,000
 To srce je srce koje izgara od ljubavi za Gospodina.

333
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:20,200
 To je srce koje izgara od ljubavi za druge.

334
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:24,440
 I upravo zbog toga Gospodin kaže,

335
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:29,920
 izgubili ste svoju prvu ljubav.

336
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:35,020
 I što Gospodin traži od nas?

337
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:37,040
 The next two words, verse 5,

338
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:39,200
 three things.

339
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,800
 Verse 9.

340
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,160
 Verse 5, three things.

341
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,660
 Gospodin traži od nas tri stvari.

342
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:51,840
 On kaže, prvo spomeni se, shvati.

343
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:56,380
 odakle si pao.

344
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:58,280
 So the Lord says,

345
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:04,600
 kad si me isprve upoznao,

346
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:06,220
 bio si skroz gore na vrhu.

347
00:31:06,220 --> 00:31:10,200
 Jer si bio jako strastven.

348
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:14,200
 Izgarao si od ljubavi za mene.

349
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:15,340
 A gospodin kaže,

350
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:22,160
 pogledaj gdje si pao danas,

351
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:23,600
 nakon 25 godina.

352
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:25,720
 So the first thing that we need to do

353
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,940
 is to realize.

354
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:30,500
 And the second.

355
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:33,100
 Repent.

356
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:35,280
 The Lord says,

357
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:35,620
 ok,

358
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:37,160
 ok,

359
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:39,060
 you have fallen from there,

360
00:31:39,060 --> 00:31:39,600
 but

361
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:41,120
 bog kaže u redu,

362
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:42,460
 ti si pao dozgo,

363
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:44,580
 but you need to repent.

364
00:31:44,580 --> 00:31:46,180
 Ali se trebaš obratiti.

365
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:47,520
 And the third thing,

366
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:53,000
 start doing the things you did at first.

367
00:31:53,380 --> 00:31:55,640
 započni činiti prva djela.

368
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,780
 Now,

369
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:59,320
 don't be desperate if you have lost the first love.

370
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:00,420
 Dakle,

371
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:02,840
 mi smo izgubili tu prvu ljubav,

372
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,020
 Bog to vidi.

373
00:32:04,020 --> 00:32:04,400
 Yeah,

374
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,420
 the Lord is giving us two,

375
00:32:06,420 --> 00:32:08,500
 three important steps.

376
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:11,420
 i Bog nam daje tri jako bitna koraka.

377
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,540
 Realize,

378
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:13,580
 shvatiti,

379
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:14,980
 repent,

380
00:32:14,980 --> 00:32:16,040
 pokajati se,

381
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:16,980
 obratiti se,

382
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:22,740
 i započeti činiti prva djela.

383
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:24,180
 Aleluja.

384
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:26,120
 Aleluja.

385
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:28,560
 Shall we raise our hands?

386
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:32,400
 Just,

387
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:36,060
 just think within your hearts.

388
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:41,520
 When did I meet the Lord?

389
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:46,500
 How many years ago?

390
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:48,600
 koliko godina je to bilo?

391
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:53,500
 And how was my love for the Lord that time?

392
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:57,680
 How passionate?

393
00:32:57,680 --> 00:33:03,220
 And where do I find myself today?

394
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:07,040
 How I become cold?

395
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:10,860
 How I become lukewarm?

396
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:14,780
 And then,

397
00:33:14,780 --> 00:33:16,140
 I need to repent.

398
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:18,180
 onda se trebamo

399
00:33:18,180 --> 00:33:19,660
 pokajati i obratiti.

400
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:21,200
 The Lord is calling me

401
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,340
 to repentance today.

402
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:23,980
 Gospodin me poziva

403
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:24,680
 još danas

404
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:25,640
 da se obrati.

405
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,880
 And the Lord is saying,

406
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:28,560
 start doing the things

407
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:30,160
 you did at first.

408
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,500
 I Gospodin mi kaže,

409
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:33,440
 počni činiti prva djela.

410
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,780
 so shall we take a decision today?

411
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:38,000
 Hoćemo li danas to započeti?

412
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:39,200
 Yes, Lord,

413
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:40,400
 we want to repent.

414
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:45,700
 We want to start doing the things

415
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:46,820
 we did at first.

416
00:33:46,820 --> 00:33:49,300
 želimo započeti činiti prva djela.

417
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:52,640
 Amen.

418
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:55,840
 You know,

419
00:33:55,840 --> 00:33:56,660
 one of the prayers

420
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,480
 that I make

421
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,380
 every day

422
00:33:58,380 --> 00:33:59,740
 in my personal prayer

423
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:00,600
 is this.

424
00:34:00,600 --> 00:34:09,300
 I just look at the Lord

425
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:13,100
 and I tell the Lord,

426
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:15,040
 Lord, I love you.

427
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:15,480
 kaže mu,

428
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,040
 Bože,

429
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:16,980
 volim te.

430
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:18,960
 It may be a simple prayer.

431
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:22,980
 But for me,

432
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,780
 it matters so much

433
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:28,520
 to tell the Lord

434
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,320
 every day.

435
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:32,420
 Lord, I love you

436
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:36,000
 because all that I do

437
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,640
 for him

438
00:34:36,640 --> 00:34:40,320
 has to be

439
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:42,580
 an outcome

440
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:44,120
 of my love for him.

441
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:45,220
 sve to mora biti

442
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:46,560
 rezultat mojej ljubavi

443
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:47,200
 za njega.

444
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:48,900
 If I don't love him,

445
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:50,500
 ako ne volim Boga,

446
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:52,460
 then all that I do

447
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:53,900
 becomes useless.

448
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:55,940
 Sve ono što ja budem činio

449
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:57,180
 bit će beskorisno.

450
00:34:57,180 --> 00:35:02,340
 Kada je Bog pozvao Petra

451
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:07,560
 i kada je učinio njega

452
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:09,020
 prvim papom

453
00:35:09,020 --> 00:35:13,160
 u Ivanovom evanđelju

454
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:15,560
 21. poglavlje,

455
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:19,980
 ima tamo jedan

456
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:21,080
 prekrasan prizor

457
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:26,000
 peta se dakle vratio

458
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,260
 nakon ribarenja

459
00:35:27,260 --> 00:35:31,040
 dakle, on je vjerojatno

460
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:36,660
 izvlačio mrežu,

461
00:35:36,660 --> 00:35:40,020
 brod je uplovljavao,

462
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:44,060
 a Isus je već bio na obali

463
00:35:44,060 --> 00:35:44,980
 i on je spremio

464
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:46,140
 doručak za njih.

465
00:35:46,140 --> 00:35:49,560
 I dok im je posluživao

466
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,240
 doručak,

467
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:54,580
 pitao je Petra

468
00:35:54,580 --> 00:35:59,700
 prije nego što je od njega

469
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:02,240
 imenovao prvim papom,

470
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:05,980
 pitao ga je samo jedno pitanje,

471
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:08,220
 Šimune,

472
00:36:08,220 --> 00:36:12,220
 Sine Jonin,

473
00:36:12,220 --> 00:36:15,180
 ljubiš li me?

